tion: absolute; top: 1px; left: 1px; text-align: right;">20</div></div></div><canvas class="flot-overlay" width="739" height="300" style="direction: ltr; position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 0px; width: 739.5px; height: 300px;"></canvas></div>
